                        <p><strong>Creative Director</strong></p>
                        <p>Shaira designs our brand experience and product collections with a focus on modern style, function, and student-friendly usability.</p>
                    </article>
                    <article class="team-card">
                        <div class="team-photo"><img src="{{ asset('team/Yannah_CEL.png') }}" alt="Yannah Dela Vega - Customer Experience Lead" loading="lazy"></div>
                        <h3>Yannah Dela Vega</h3>
                        <p><strong>Customer Experience Lead</strong></p>
                        <p>Yannah ensures every customer interaction is helpful and fast, from product questions to order follow-ups and support.</p>
                    </article>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="section testimonials" id="testimonials">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="section-head">
                    <p class="eyebrow">What our customers say</p>
                    <h2>Trusted by students & professionals</h2>
                    <p>Join thousands of satisfied customers who rely on Pacunla for their school and office supplies.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="testimonials-grid">
                    <article class="testimonial-card">
                        <div class="testimonial-content">
                            <p>"Pacunla has everything I need for my architecture studies. The quality is excellent and the prices are unbeatable. My go-to for all my supplies!"</p>
                        </div>
