                        </div>
                        <div class="testimonial-author">
                            <img src="{{ asset('sample-users/sample_user2.png') }}" width="50" height="50" alt="High School Teacher" loading="lazy">
                            <div>
                                <strong>Michael R.</strong>
                                <span>High School Teacher</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </article>
                    <article class="testimonial-card">
                        <div class="testimonial-content">
                            <p>"Perfect for my home office setup. Professional quality supplies at student-friendly prices. Fast shipping and great customer service too!"</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="testimonial-author">
                            <img src="{{ asset('sample-users/sample_user3.png') }}" width="50" height="50" alt="Graphic Designer" loading="lazy">
